### TL 1차 승인 (PENDING → APPROVED)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/kms/tl/approval/{{articleId}}/approve
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "approverId": 1774590584056408,
  "reviewComment": "내용 검토 완료. 1차 승인합니다."
}

### TL 반려 (PENDING → REJECTED)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/kms/tl/approval/{{articleId}}/reject
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reviewComment": "내용이 불충분합니다. 보완 후 재제출 바랍니다."
}
